#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">From the <b>Inventory App</b>, you can effortlessly "
"manage your <b>stock levels</b>, handle <b>deliveries</b>, and process "
"<b>returns</b>.</span><span class=\"h2-fs\"/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">ຜ່ານ <b>ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory)</b>, ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການ <b>ລະດັ"
"ບສິນຄ້າຄົງສັງ</b>, ດຳເນີນການ <b>ຈັດສົ່ງ</b>, ແລະ ປະມວນຜົນ <b>ການສົ່ງຄືນ</b> ໄດ້ຢ່າງງ່າຍດາ"
"ຍ.</span><span class=\"h2-fs\"/><br/>"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">From the <b>Purchases App </b> you can define your "
"minimum stock level per product, process order make the follow "
"up</span><span class=\"h2-fs\"/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"h6-fs\">ຜ່ານ <b>ແອັບການຈັດຊື້ (Purchases)</b> ທ່ານສາມາດກຳນົດລະດັບສິນຄ້າຄົງ"
"ສັງຂັ້ນຕ່ຳຕໍ່ຜະລິດຕະພັນ, ປະມວນຜົນການສັ່ງຊື້ ແລະ ຕິດຕາມຜົນ</span><span class=\"h2-fs\"/><br/>"

