#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo helps you perfectly tailor your website to your clients' needs. Easily "
"integrate your internal policies, customize the contact form, showcase your "
"latest arrivals, create an inspiration blog, and much more!"
msgstr ""
"Odoo ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທ່ານປັບແຕ່ງເວັບໄຊໃຫ້ກົງກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງລູກຄ້າໄດ້ຢ່າງສົມບູນ. ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ນະໂຍບາຍພາຍໃນຮ້າ"
"ນ, ປັບແຕ່ງແບບຟອມຕິດຕໍ່, ສະແດງສິນຄ້າໃໝ່, ສ້າງບລັອກແຮງບັນດານໃຈ ແລະ ອື່ນໆອີກຫຼາຍຢ່າງ!"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to <b>manage your "
"entire business from your phone</b>.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"Odoo ໄດ້ຖືກຮວມເຂົ້າເປັນແອັບດຽວ. ດາວໂຫຼດເພື່ອ <b>ຈັດການທຸລະກິດທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານຜ່ານມືຖື</b>.<br/>"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo offers a complete solution to enhance efficiency and improve customer "
"satisfaction across all your furniture store services."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ມອບໂຊລູຊັ່ນທີ່ຄົບວົງຈອນເພື່ອເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບ ແລະ ຄວາມເພິ່ງພໍໃຈຂອງລູກຄ້າໃນທຸກການບໍລິການຂອງຮ້ານເຟີ"
"ນີເຈີຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນ, ນີ້ເປັນພຽງພາບລວມຂອງຟີເຈີໃນແພັກເກັດນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລຶບ ຫຼື ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ ແລະ "
"ທົດລອງໃຊ້ງານທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ຕາມໃຈ!"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once confirmed, <b>Purchase Orders are automatically created</b> in the "
"Purchase App."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ, <b>ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ</b> ໃນແອັບການຈັດຊື້ (Purchase)."

