"store inventory and your website's online catalog."
msgstr ""
"ໂມດູນນີ້ຊ່ວຍເພີ່ມປະສິດທິພາບການດຳເນີນງານປະຈຳວັນຂອງຮ້ານເຟີນີເຈີຂອງທ່ານ ໂດຍການຈັດການການຂາຍສິນຄ້າ, "
"ຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ຂອງລູກຄ້າ, ລວມທັງການຈັດການສາງສິນຄ້າໃນຮ້ານ ແລະ ລາຍການສິນຄ້າອອນລາຍໃນເວັບໄຊຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເປັ"
"ນລະບົບ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_2244
msgid ""
"Timeless\n"
"                                            Furniture for Inspired Living"
msgstr ""
"ເຟີນີເຈີ\n"
"                                            ທີ່ຢູ່ເໜືອກິດຈະການ ເພື່ອຊີວິດທີ່ມີແຮງບັນດານໃຈ"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To efficiently manage your product catalog you can create with variants and "
"<strong>publish them online</strong>. Additionally, you can establish "
"various <strong>categories</strong> for both your website's display and your"
" internal organizational needs."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອຈັດການລາຍການສິນຄ້າຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ, ທ່ານສາມາດສ້າງສິນຄ້າທີ່ມີຮູບແບບຍ່ອຍ ແລະ <strong>ເຜີຍແຜ່ທາ"
"ງອອນລາຍ</strong>. ນອກຈາກນັ້ນ, ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດກຳນົດ <strong>ໝວດໝູ່</strong> ຕ່າງໆ ສຳລັບທັງກ"
"ານສະແດງຜົນໃນເວັບໄຊ ແລະ ການຈັດການພາຍໃນອົງກອນ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To get a rapid understanding of the processes this Odoo package offers, you "
"can execute the following flows and configure the settings to suit your "
"furniture store."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອໃຫ້ເຂົ້າໃຈຂັ້ນຕອນຕ່າງໆທີ່ແພັກເກັດ Odoo ນີ້ມີໃຫ້ໂດຍໄວ, ທ່ານສາມາດທົດລອງຂັ້ນຕອນການເຮັດວຽກຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ ແລ"
"ະ ຕັ້ງຄ່າໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຮ້ານເຟີນີເຈີຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:product.public.category,website_description:furniture_store.product_public_category_4
msgid "Transform your bedroom into a sanctuary with our elegant beds."
msgstr ""
"ປ່ຽນຫ້ອງນອນຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເປັນບ່ອນພັກຜ່ອນທີ່ແສນສະບາຍດ້ວຍຕຽງນອນທີ່ສວຍງາມຂອງພວກເຮົາ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Use the <b>Manufacturing App</b> if you plan to sell products as kits, "
"simplifying complex assemblies."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ <b>ແອັບການຜະລິດ (Manufacturing)</b> ຖ້າທ່ານມີແຜນຈະຂາຍສິນຄ້າເປັນຊຸດ (Kit), ເພື່ອເຮັດໃຫ້ກ"
"ານປະກອບສິນຄ້າທີ່ຊັບຊ້ອນກາຍເປັນເລື່ອງງ່າຍ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Validate the transaction."
msgstr "ຢືນຢັນທຸລະກຳ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model:product.template,name:furniture_store.product_template_26
msgid "Vintage Table"
msgstr "ໂຕະ Vintage"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_2244
msgid ""
"We offer a 30-day return policy for\n"
"                                                                all furniture items. Products must\n"
"                                                                be in their original condition,\n"
"                                                                unused, and include the receipt or\n"
"                                                                proof of purchase. Refunds are\n"
"                                                                processed within 5-7 business days\n"
"                                                                after we receive the returned item."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາມີນັກໂຍບາຍການສົ່ງຄືນສິນຄ້າພາຍໃນ 30 ວັນ ສຳລັບ\n"
"                                                                ເຟີນີເຈີທຸກລາຍກາ"
"ນ. ສິນຄ້າຕ້ອງ\n"
"                                                                ຢູ່ໃນສະພາບເດີມ, "
"ບໍ່ໄດ້ຜ່ານການໃຊ້ງານ,\n"
"                                                                ແລະ ຕ້ອງມີໃບບິນ "
"ຫຼື ຫຼັກຖານການຊື້.\n"
"                                                                ການຄືນເງິນຈະຖືກດ"
"ຳເນີນການພາຍໃນ 5-7 ວັນເຮັດວຽກ\n"
"                                                                ຫຼັງຈາກທີ່ພວກເຮົາໄ"
"ດ້ຮັບສິນຄ້າຄືນ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_3972
msgid ""
"We'd love to hear from you! If you have any\n"
"                                            questions, feedback, or need assistance, please feel\n"
"                                            free to reach out to us using the contact details\n"
"                                            provided. Our team is here to help and will respond as\n"
"                                            soon as possible. Thank you for getting in touch!"
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາຍິນດີຮັບຟັງຈາກທ່ານ! ຖ້າທ່ານມີ\n"
"                                            ຄຳຖາມ, ຄຳຕິຊົມ ຫຼື ຕ້ອງການຄວາມຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ, "
"ກະລຸນາ\n"
"                                            ຕິດຕໍ່ຫາພວກເຮົາຕາມຂໍ້ມູນການຕິດຕໍ່ທີ່ໃຫ້ໄວ້.\n"
"                                            ທີມງານຂອງພວກເຮົາຍິນດີໃຫ້ບໍລິການ ແລະ ຈະຕອ"
"ບກັບໂດຍໄວທີ່ສຸດ.\n"
"                                            ຂອບໃຈທີ່ຕິດຕໍ່ຫາພວກເຮົາ!"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_2244
msgid ""
"We're here to assist you,\n"
"                                                day and night."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາຍິນດີຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອທ່ານ,\n"
"                                                ທັງກາງເວັນ ແລະ ກາງຄືນ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_2244
msgid ""
"We’re dedicated to providing quick\n"
"                                                                and effective solutions to ensure\n"
"                                                                your satisfaction."
msgstr ""
"ພວກເຮົາມຸ່ງໝັ້ນທີ່ຈະມອບວິທີແກ້ໄຂທີ່ວ່ອງໄວ\n"
"                                                                ແລະ ມີປະສິດທິພາ"
"ບ ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນ\n"
"                                                                ຄວາມເພິ່ງພໍໃຈຂອງ"
"ທ່ານ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When a customer fills out your contact form, Odoo automatically creates an "
"<b>opportunity</b> in the <b>CRM App</b>. This makes it simple to "
"communicate with the client, address their specific needs, and even "
"<b>create a tailored quotation</b> directly from the CRM."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອລູກຄ້າຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນໃນແບບຟອມຕິດຕໍ່, Odoo ຈະສ້າງ <b>ໂອກາດການຂາຍ (opportunity)</b> ໃນ <b>ແອັ"
"ບ CRM</b> ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ນີ້ຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ການສື່ສານກັບລູກຄ້າ, ການຕອບສະໜອງຄວາມຕ້ອງການສະເພາະ ແລະ ກ"
"ານ <b>ສ້າງໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ</b> ເປັນເລື່ອງງ່າຍໂດຍກົງຈາກ CRM."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_2244
msgid ""
"With a long-standing tradition in furniture\n"
"                                            craftsmanship, we combine modern design with practical\n"
"                                            use. Our mission is to create pieces that are both\n"
"                                            beautiful and functional, ensuring each item enhances\n"
"                                            your living space while providing comfort and style."
msgstr ""
"ດ້ວຍປະສົບການອັນຍາວນານໃນງານຝີມືເຟີນີເຈີ,\n"
"                                            ພວກເຮົາໄດ້ຮວມເອົາການອອກແບບທີ່ທັນສະໄໝເຂົ້າ"
"ກັບການໃຊ້ງານຕົວຈິງ.\n"
"                                            ພາລະກິດຂອງພວກເຮົາຄືການສ້າງສັນຜົນງານທີ່ທັງສ"
"ວຍງາມ ແລະ\n"
"                                            ໃຊ້ປະໂຫຍດໄດ້ດີ, ເພື່ອຮັບປະກັນວ່າແຕ່ລະຊິ້ນສ່ວນ"
"ຈະຊ່ວຍຍົກລະດັບ\n"
"                                            ພື້ນທີ່ຢູ່ອາໄສຂອງທ່ານ ພ້ອມທັງມອບຄວາມສະບາຍ "
"ແລະ ສະໄຕລ໌ທີ່ໂດດເດັ່ນ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Within the <strong>Inventory App</strong>"
msgstr "ພາຍໃນ <strong>ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory)</strong>"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Within the <strong>Invenyory App</strong>"
msgstr "ພາຍໃນ <strong>ແອັບສາງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory)</strong>"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Within the <strong>Purchase App</strong>"
msgstr "ພາຍໃນ <strong>ແອັບການຈັດຊື້ (Purchase)</strong>"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model:product.template,name:furniture_store.product_template_20
msgid "Wood effect"
msgstr "ລາຍໄມ້"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປຶກສາຫາລືກ່ຽວກັບການຕິດຕັ້ງ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານ ຫຼື ຕ້ອງການຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມບໍ່?"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can <b>show the order's progress on a screen</b> for your customers to "
"see!"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດ <b>ສະແດງຄວາມຄືບໜ້າຂອງລາຍການສັ່ງຊື້ເທິງໜ້າຈໍ</b> ເພື່ອໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າເຫັນໄດ້!"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ໄດ້ຈາກໜ້າຈໍຫຼັກຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can merge multiple Purchase Orders for the same vendor as long as they "
"haven't been confirmed yet.<strong/><b/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດຮວມໃບສັ່ງຊື້ຫຼາຍໃບສຳລັບຜູ້ສະໜອງດຽວກັນໄດ້ ຕາບໃດທີ່ໃບສັ່ງຊື້ນັ້ນຍັງບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ຮັບການຢືນຢັ"
"ນ.<strong/><b/><br/>"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can process <strong>partial deliveries </strong>by adjusting the "
"quantity. Odoo will automatically generate a backorder for any remaining "
"items.<b/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດປະມວນຜົນ <strong>ການຈັດສົ່ງບາງສ່ວນ </strong> ໄດ້ໂດຍການປັບຈຳນວນ. Odoo ຈະສ້າງລາ"
"ຍການສັ່ງສິນຄ້າຄ້າງສົ່ງ (backorder) ສຳລັບສິນຄ້າທີ່ຍັງເຫຼືອໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ.<b/><br/>"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can process all inventory transactions directly from the <strong>Barcode"
" App</strong> if you're using a <strong>mobile device or "
"scanner.</strong><b/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດປະມວນຜົນທຸກທຸລະກຳສາງສິນຄ້າໄດ້ໂດຍກົງຈາກ <strong>ແອັບບາໂຄດ (Barcode)</strong> ຖ້"
"າທ່ານໃຊ້ <strong>ມືຖື ຫຼື ເຄື່ອງສະແກນ.</strong><b/><br/>"

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.ir_ui_view_2244
msgid ""
"You can reach our customer support\n"
"                                                                team by emailing\n"
"                                                                support@generationfurniture.com,\n"
"                                                                calling +1 555-555-1234, or using\n"
"                                                                the live chat feature on our\n"
"                                                                website. Our dedicated team is\n"
"                                                                available 24/7 to assist with any\n"
"                                                                inquiries or issues."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດຕິດຕໍ່ຝ່າຍບໍລິການລູກຄ້າ\n"
"                                                                ຂອງພວກເຮົາໄດ້ທາ"
"ງອີເມລ\n"
"                                                                "
"support@generationfurniture.com,\n"
"                                                                ໂທ +1 555-"
"555-1234, ຫຼື ໃຊ້\n"
"                                                                ຟີເຈີໄລຟ໌ແຊັດ "
"(live chat) ໃນເວັບໄຊ\n"
"                                                                ຂອງພວກເຮົາ. ທີມ"
"ງານຂອງພວກເຮົາຍິນດີ\n"
"                                                                ໃຫ້ບໍລິການຕະຫຼອດ "
"24 ຊົ່ວໂມງ ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອ\n"
"                                                                ທຸກຄຳຖາມ ຫຼື ບັນຫ"
"າຕ່າງໆ."

#. module: furniture_store
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:furniture_store.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries"
" &gt; Upgrade your Library package and select the relevant checkbox"
msgstr ""
